data.description: Come make this one yours today! This 3 bed, 2 bath, 4 side brick ranch style home sits on a .64 acre level corner lot in a quiet, well-kept neighborhood with large lots directly off of Hwy. 78, within minutes of all the great cities of Snellville, Stone Mountain, and Loganville have to offer. Fenced backyard with brick patio, garden area, and plenty of space to play or relax under mature trees. Side entry two car garage. The roof was replaced in 2018. Original fixtures throughout, including hardwood floors, resilient tile work, unique countertops, and cast iron tub. The updated HVAC is in great condition, newer dishwasher, and an entire house water filtration system in place. Floor-to-ceiling windows in the great room and multiple storage closets in the hallway. The kitchen has plenty of cabinets for storage, a deep double sink, and granite countertops. No HOA.
